<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>After treatment with Matt my digestion is completely different! I can eat moderate amountsÂ  of wheat and dairy without pain. All the meals I eat digest easily â€“ I donâ€™t get cramps,Â  bloating or pain anymore during or after eating. My biggest improvement was not havingÂ  flatulence during the day!</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>These changes make me feel more confident in myself. I feel that I can wear the clothes IÂ  want to wear without worrying about bloating. My energy levels have improved so I feelÂ  better throughout the day. I feel more alive, happy and generally get more out of my day.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Matt is so lovely to work with. He is very kind and takes the time to analyze all of yourÂ  symptoms. The food plan is easy to follow and Matt takes into account your dietaryÂ  preferences. I had a great experience working with Matt and his support through the wholeÂ  process will not be forgotten.</p>
