<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Matt was the firstÂ  health professional who helped me search for the root cause of my symptoms,Â  rather than just putting a â€œbandaidâ€ on them, and I am so grateful for hisÂ  guidance. I would highly recommend Matt, if you have any underlying gut issues.Â  He might make you give up wine temporarily, but heâ€™s a nice guy!</p>
