<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>The stomachÂ  discomfort would come and go less, and became less intense. After months of treatment,Â  the discomfort was no more. I was over the moon and in debt to Matt for his counsel. HeÂ  was always professional, and has strong intuition for gut related conditions. The path toÂ  recovery is not short, but it must be taken if you want to restore your gutâ€™s microbiome</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" module_class="testi-cli" _builder_version="4.0.6" custom_padding="0px||||false|false"][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.0.6"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="4.0.6"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.0.6" header_2_font="Montserrat|600|||||||" header_2_text_color="#167d7f" header_2_font_size="39px"]<h2>Ben (NSW, Australia)</h2>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.7.7" text_font="Montserrat|600|||||||" text_text_color="#000000" text_font_size="24px" text_line_height="45px" text_orientation="center" custom_padding="30px||0px||false|false"]<h3><strong>â€˜After months of treatment, the discomfort was no more. I was over the moon andÂ  in debt to Matt for his counsel. He was always professional, and has strongÂ  intuition for gut related conditions.â€™</strong></h3>
<h3><strong>BenÂ Â </strong></h3>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.0.6" custom_padding="0px||||false|false"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="4.0.6"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.0.6" text_font="Montserrat||||||||" text_text_color="#4a4a4a" text_font_size="16px" text_line_height="26px" custom_padding="|||20px|false|false" border_width_left="5px" border_color_left="#9b9b9b"]<p>During a course of Roaccutane treatment I began to suffer extreme side effects whichÂ  included; severe bloating that never seemed to subside and which became veryÂ  uncomfortable, loss of appetite, the feeling of being full after a small meal, irregular bowelÂ  movements and constipation and a restrictive diet. Although I am an extremely activeÂ  person i did not feel healthy, the bloating made me feel like I was carrying extra weight andÂ  I often felt lethargic. After seeing Matt and commencing the treatment recommended byÂ  him I immediately saw results, over the course of 3-4 months the bloating and constipationÂ  completely disappeared, i was able to reintroduce all food groups back into my diet thatÂ  generally I could not eat prior to treatment.</p>
<p>I have completed my treatment with Matt and my digestive health has never been betterÂ  with no signs of any symptoms and I am free to eat anything I want to without worrying!Â </p>
<p>I would recommend Matt to anyone experiencing similar symptoms, he thoroughly explainsÂ  each phase of the treatment, carefully tracks your progress over the course of theÂ  treatment, makes any adjustments necessary and is always on hand to answer anyÂ  questions and is well worth the time and money especially if like me it affects your day toÂ  day life.Â </p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" module_class="testi-cli" _builder_version="4.0.6" custom_padding="0px||||false|false"][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.0.6"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="4.0.6"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.0.6" header_2_font="Montserrat|600|||||||" header_2_text_color="#167d7f" header_2_font_size="39px"]<h2>Meera (NSW, Australia)Â  </h2>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.7.7" text_font="Montserrat|600|||||||" text_text_color="#000000" text_font_size="24px" text_line_height="45px" text_orientation="center" custom_padding="30px||||false|false"]<h3><strong>â€˜I have completed my treatment with Matt and my digestive health has neverÂ  been better with no signs of any symptoms and I am free to eat anything I want toÂ  without worrying!â€™</strong></h3>
<h3><strong>Meera</strong></h3>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.0.6" custom_padding="0px||||false|false"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="4.0.6"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.0.6" text_font="Montserrat||||||||" text_text_color="#4a4a4a" text_font_size="16px" text_line_height="26px" custom_padding="|||20px|false|false" border_width_left="5px" border_color_left="#9b9b9b"]<p>Recommend Matt to anyone having trouble with their gut and at a loss with unhelpfulÂ  doctors. Matt gives a highly effective questionnaire to narrow down your symptoms. AfterÂ  being ill for over two years with no answers Matt gave me tests to determine what I had,Â  something no doctor bothered to do previously. The answer ended up being something IÂ  had never even heard of. Matt is very knowledgeable and caring of his patients. He put meÂ  on herbal medication and a strict diet but all I can say is follow it to a tee â€“ he knows exactlyÂ  what he is doing. Iâ€™m happy to say he helped heal me from the inside out and I havenâ€™t beenÂ  this happy with my health ever before. Canâ€™t thank him enough. If this sounds like somethingÂ  you can relate to do not hesitate to see Matt!Â </p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" module_class="testi-cli" _builder_version="4.0.6" custom_padding="0px||||false|false"][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.0.6"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="4.0.6"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.0.6" header_2_font="Montserrat|600|||||||" header_2_text_color="#167d7f" header_2_font_size="39px"]<h2>Emma (NSW, Australia)</h2>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.7.7" text_font="Montserrat|600|||||||" text_text_color="#000000" text_font_size="24px" text_line_height="45px" text_orientation="center" custom_padding="30px||||false|false"]<h3><strong>`I'm happy to say he helped heal me from the inside out and I havenâ€™t been thisÂ  happy with my health ever before. Canâ€™t thank him enough. If this sounds like something you can relate to do not hesitate to see Matt!â€™Â </strong></h3>
<h3><strong>Emma</strong></h3>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.0.6" custom_padding="0px||||false|false"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="4.0.6"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.0.6" text_font="Montserrat||||||||" text_text_color="#4a4a4a" text_font_size="16px" text_line_height="26px" custom_padding="|||20px|false|false" border_width_left="5px" border_color_left="#9b9b9b"]<p>I came to see Matt with a long list of symptoms that I intuitively knew were related to poorÂ  gut health. My symptoms included: brain fog which consisted of an inability to concentrate,Â  poor memory and a general cognitive slowness; chronic fatigue which consisted ofÂ  perpetual tiredness and absolutely no energy; chronic stomach pains, reflux and gas; andÂ  irregular bowel movements. Overall, I felt physically exhausted and extremely unwell whenÂ  I first came to see Matt. My immune system was also weak which meant that I wasÂ  vulnerable to catching any kind of bug going around. After committing to the treatment planÂ  Matt set out for me, which continued over a period of around 6-7 months, I can honestly sayÂ  that I am now cured and no longer suffer from any of the symptoms mentioned above.  IÂ  havenâ€™t felt this healthy for years â€“ I feel amazing! I would highly recommend Matt toÂ  anyone who is experiencing poor gut health. He is incredibly knowledgeable and uses anÂ  evidence based approach to healing. He is able to discover the root cause of symptoms soÂ  that treatment can be tailored to combating the problem at its source. I can now moveÂ  forward with a quality of life that I was unable to achieve â€“ due to chronic illness â€“ for soÂ  long and this is something that I am immensely grateful for.</p>
<p>Thanks again for everything. I honestly do feel amazing!Â </p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" module_class="testi-cli" _builder_version="4.0.6" custom_padding="0px||||false|false"][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.0.6"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="4.0.6"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.0.6" header_2_font="Montserrat|600|||||||" header_2_text_color="#167d7f" header_2_font_size="39px"]<h2>Dennielle (NSW, Australia)</h2>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.7.7" text_font="Montserrat|600|||||||" text_text_color="#000000" text_font_size="24px" text_line_height="45px" text_orientation="center" custom_padding="30px||||false|false"]<h3><strong>â€˜ I can honestly say that I am now cured and no longer suffer from any of the symptomsÂ  mentioned above. I havenâ€™t felt this healthy for years â€“ I feel amazing! I would highlyÂ  recommend Matt to anyone who is experiencing poor gut health.â€™</strong></h3>
<h3><strong>DennielleÂ </strong></h3>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.7.7" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="4.7.7" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.7.7" _module_preset="default" text_font_size="16px"]<div>
<p class="v1MsoNormal"><span style="color: #333333;">Coming</span> from a medical background, I took the conventional medical approach when my IBS symptoms, over a number of years, became too severe to cope with.</p>
</div>
<div>
<p class="v1MsoNormal">My General Practitioner and Gastroenterologist led me to the low-FODMAP diet, that is amazing for symptoms but not a long term solution.</p>
</div>
<div>
<p class="v1MsoNormal">Functional medicine addressed my issues with digestion and my multiple deficiencies, but I was still very symptomatic if I strayed from my very restricted diet.</p>
</div>
<div>
<p class="v1MsoNormal">My own research led me to SIBO (Small Intestinal Bacterial Overgrowth), as a possible cause of my IBS, but I struggled to find a practitioner that is current with all its emerging research and testing.</p>
</div>
<div>
<p class="v1MsoNormal">After finding Matt's clinic and the 15 min free phone consultation, that he offers, I was hopeful (and correct) that he was the practitioner that could move me forward from my impasse.</p>
</div>
<div>
<p class="v1MsoNormal">Matt is very professional and up-to-date with all of the latest research and treatment plans. My journey to health was not short but Matt was always available for questions, happy to adjust treatment, and always encouraging.</p>
</div>
<div>
<p class="v1MsoNormal">These gut issues can be complex to treat but I am so thankful that I found Matt to guide me through to my current health.</p>
<h3>Â </h3>
<h2><strong><span style="color: #008080;">Sandra (NSW, Australia)</span></strong></h2>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
</div>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.7.7" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="4.7.7" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.7.7" _module_preset="default"]<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>'Matt is very professional and up-to-date with all of the latest research and treatment plans. My journey to health was not short but Matt was always available for questions, happy to adjust treatment, and always encouraging.'</strong></h3>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Sandra</strong></h3>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.0.6" custom_padding="0px||||false|false"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="4.0.6"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.0.6" text_font="Montserrat||||||||" text_text_color="#4a4a4a" text_font_size="16px" text_line_height="26px" custom_padding="|||20px|false|false" border_width_left="5px" border_color_left="#9b9b9b"]<p>I got an infection in my stomach from something Iâ€™ve been exposed to or ate, then my lifeÂ  changed dramatically afterwards!Â 
I used to eat everything & had no problems with food or digestion until this infection, I thenÂ  suddenly stopped digesting food, it would sit there for days, ferment and cause severeÂ  chronic constipation & bloating associated with extreme pain. I couldnâ€™t eat properly whichÂ  had a significant effect on my personal life, work, concentration & pretty much everything.Â </p>
<p>I have been to many doctors & done many tests with only disappointment & noÂ  improvement. I was desperate & depressed, my life turned upside down until i searched theÂ  internet & found information about Matt and the Digestive Wellness Clinic and only thenÂ  when I started to see light at the end of the tunnel after I was told that Iâ€™d just have to liveÂ  like this, something I refused to believe.Â </p>
<p>Matt diagnosed me with SIBO and that explained the fatigue, nutrient malabsorption and allÂ  the symptoms I was experiencing. Matt put me on a treatment program of naturalÂ </p>
<p>supplements and diet that I followed with his support and guidance throughout the journey.Â  I started noticing improvements after about 2 months and after 6 months I could say that IÂ  was completely back to normal. Matt was always very supportive & responsive to myÂ  queries, always calm, always positive and reassuring. He gave me strength to keep goingÂ  and complete the journey until full recovery, until i got my life back! Iâ€™m back to cycling, Iâ€™veÂ  got much more energy now to spend good time with the family, to work properly and doÂ  whatever I want!Â 
I would recommend Matt to those who suffer from any gut issue & all those who reachedÂ  dead ends and tried everything without success. Matt is knowledgeable and experienced,Â  he customises the treatment according to oneâ€™s conditions and needs. He is veryÂ  understanding, caring and a true professional!Â </p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" module_class="testi-cli" _builder_version="4.0.6" custom_padding="0px||||false|false"][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.0.6"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="4.0.6"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.0.6" header_2_font="Montserrat|600|||||||" header_2_text_color="#167d7f" header_2_font_size="39px"]<h2>Dina (NSW, Australia)Â  </h2>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.7.7" text_font="Montserrat|600|||||||" text_text_color="#000000" text_font_size="24px" text_line_height="45px" text_orientation="center" custom_padding="30px||||false|false"]<h3>â€˜<strong>He gave me strength to keep going and complete the journey until full recovery,Â  until i got my life back! Iâ€™m back to cycling, Iâ€™ve got much more energy now toÂ  spend good time with the family, to work properly and do whatever I want!â€™</strong></h3>
<p><strong>Dina</strong></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.0.6" custom_padding="0px||||false|false"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="4.0.6"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.0.6" text_font="Montserrat||||||||" text_text_color="#4a4a4a" text_font_size="16px" text_line_height="26px" custom_padding="|||20px|false|false" border_width_left="5px" border_color_left="#9b9b9b"]<p>After receiving treatment and testing  from Matthew Douglas, almost all my symptoms haveÂ  resolved. I did suffer from sudden weight loss, anxiety, depression, disturbed sleep, IBS andÂ  many more embarrassing symptoms, my life was in a painful mess, physically and mentally.Â  Matthew recommended I take a comprehensive stool test which I did and the test hadÂ  proven I had a very bad Candida and Klebsiella overgrowth after a very strong antibioticsÂ  treatment a year before for a parasite Blastocystis Hominis and unhealthy diet habits. TheÂ  Blasto was gone but I had let the bad yeast and bacteria in by killing most of my goodÂ  bacteria.  I thought I would have to live with these symptoms for the rest of my life. TheÂ  Digestive Wellness Clinic has turned my life around and I have not had this much energy inÂ  years along with healthy weight gain that has also improved my gym workouts. The biggestÂ  wow factor for me is that I no longer have anxiety or depression which I have had most ofÂ  my adult life!  If I could recommend one thing is that you will need patience and a lot of willÂ  power and you will get your life back. I have also been very well educated by Matt on howÂ  to live a healthy life with good diet habits and probiotics. I have my life back!!</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" module_class="testi-cli" _builder_version="4.0.6" custom_padding="0px||||false|false"][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.0.6"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="4.0.6"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.0.6" header_2_font="Montserrat|600|||||||" header_2_text_color="#167d7f" header_2_font_size="39px"]<h2>Nigel (NSW, Australia)</h2>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.7.7" text_font="Montserrat|600|||||||" text_text_color="#000000" text_font_size="24px" text_line_height="45px" text_orientation="center" custom_padding="30px||||false|false"]<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>â€˜The Digestive Wellness Clinic has turned my life around and I have not had thisÂ  much energy in years along with healthy weight gain that has also improved myÂ  gym workouts. The biggest wow factor for me is that I no longer have anxiety orÂ  depression which I have had most of my adult life!â€™</strong></h3>
<h3><strong>Nigel</strong></h3>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.0.6" custom_padding="0px||||false|false"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="4.0.6"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.0.6" text_font="Montserrat||||||||" text_text_color="#4a4a4a" text_font_size="16px" text_line_height="26px" custom_padding="|||20px|false|false" border_width_left="5px" border_color_left="#9b9b9b"]<p>During a holiday in Vietnam 2 years ago I picked up two parasites (D. Fragilis andÂ  Blastocystis hominis) which were causing:Â  </p>
<ul>
<li>frequent diarrhoea and abdominal pain</li>
<li>general fatigueÂ </li>
<li>bouts of a strange tingling/vibration through my body</li>
</ul>
<p>I had been on a gluten free diet for 4 years at this stage and had been havingÂ  episodes that were like hypoglycaemia with feelings of extreme hunger followedÂ  by sweating/dizziness that were resolved with juice or a gluten free snack bar.Â  Over a period of 18 months my GP and Gastroenterologist had treated me with 5Â  different courses of antibiotics, most of them combination courses, one with 4Â  drugs at once which made me feel more unwell than the parasites.  TheseÂ  managed to get rid of the Blastocystis but not the D. Fragilis and my symptomsÂ  were unchanged.Â  I was feeling really fed up with the ongoing diarrhoea, fatigue and generalÂ  unwellness.Â  After 6 months of treatment with Matt I am now parasite and symptom free.  IÂ  have more energy and my partner has commented that the â€œold meâ€ is now backÂ  again.Â  I am no longer getting the strange vibrations or the hypoglycaemic episodes.  Iâ€™mÂ  also introducing small amounts of gluten back into my diet eating sourdoughÂ  bread with no ill effects.Â  It was a difficult 6 months of treatment as the diet was very restrictive (especiallyÂ  over Christmas), but it was absolutely worth it!  Not only have the parasites gone,Â  but my overall gut health is vastly improved.Â  Matt is a great practitioner and I would highly recommend him.  His knowledge ofÂ  gut health is extensive and his treatments work.  He is very professional and is aÂ  great educator, providing detailed explanations so that you understand whatâ€™sÂ  happening Heâ€™s also really supportive throughout the treatment, responding veryÂ  quickly to any queries and questions.Â </p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" module_class="testi-cli" _builder_version="4.0.6" custom_padding="0px||0px||false|false"][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.0.6"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="4.0.6"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.0.6" header_2_font="Montserrat|600|||||||" header_2_text_color="#167d7f" header_2_font_size="39px"]<h2>Sally (NSW, Australia)Â </h2>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.7.7" text_font="Montserrat|600|||||||" text_text_color="#000000" text_font_size="24px" text_line_height="45px" text_orientation="center" custom_padding="30px||||false|false"]<h3><strong></strong></h3>
<h3><strong></strong></h3>
<h3><strong>â€˜After 6 months of treatment with Matt I am now parasite and symptom free. IÂ  have more energy and my partner has commented that the â€œold meâ€ is now backÂ  again.â€™</strong></h3>
<h3><strong>Sally</strong></h3>
<p><strong></strong></p>
<p><strong></strong></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" module_class="testi-cli" _builder_version="4.0.6" custom_padding="0px||||false|false"][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.0.6"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="4.0.6"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.0.6" header_2_font="Montserrat|600|||||||" header_2_text_color="#167d7f" header_2_font_size="39px"]<p><span data-rtid="ioCnj5odfEE0"><span class="r-iAx9uU8H4YBY"><span class="review-full-text">I suffered from chronic constipation and IBS for many years. I felt very unwell most of the time and very tired. Over the years, I tried western and non-western medicines, and every diet under the sun, to help resolve my symptoms. All with little to no impact. I am super grateful for Matt's guidance and wholistic approach. His approach is deeply informed and considered. Not long after staring Matt's regime, I started to feel well and I had energy. Best of all, I was regular again. I now feel really well. I highly recommend Matt from The Digestive Wellness Clinic.</span></span></span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2>Gabrielle (NSW, Australia)</h2>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.0.6" text_font="Montserrat|600|||||||" text_text_color="#000000" text_font_size="24px" text_line_height="45px" text_orientation="center" custom_padding="30px||||false|false"]<h3><strong>â€˜<span class="r-iAx9uU8H4YBY"><span class="review-full-text">Not long after staring Matt's regime, I started to feel well and I had energy. Best of all, I was regular again. I now feel really well.</span></span>â€™</strong></h3>
<h3><strong>Gabrielle</strong></h3>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" module_class="testi-cli" _builder_version="4.0.6" custom_padding="0px||||false|false"][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.0.6" custom_padding="0px||||false|false"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="4.0.6"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.7.7" text_font="Montserrat||||||||" text_text_color="#4a4a4a" text_font_size="16px" text_line_height="26px" custom_padding="|||20px|false|false" border_width_left="5px" border_color_left="#9b9b9b" inline_fonts="Georgia"]<p>After suffering from constant bloating,Â  stabbing pain in my abdomen, gas, rosacea and dealing with years of food sensitives, I decided to work with Matt after following his work for sometime. I knew I wanted to feel healthier overall and eliminate the pain and imbalances completely. After Dr.â€™s tests couldnâ€™t locate an actionable issue for my digestive symptoms, Mattâ€™s recommended tests did. Working with Matt to resolve these issues collaboratively was enlightening and supportive. It was honestly one of the best investments for my health. Recovery after working with Matt has seen me being able to live healthier, enjoy food again with friends and family and envision greater health goals for myself. I have recommended Matt to family and friends and cannot thank him enough for the invaluable expertise and support he provided.</p>
<h2>Â </h2>
<h2><strong><span style="color: #008080;">Alana (NSW, Australia)</span></strong></h2>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Â <strong><span style="font-family: inherit;">'Recovery after working with Matt has seen me being able to live healthier, enjoy food again with friends and family and envision greater health goals for myself.'</span></strong></h3>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-family: inherit;">Alana</span></strong></h3>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" _builder_version="4.0.6"][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.0.6" custom_padding="0px|||||"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="4.0.6"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.7.7" custom_margin="-23px|||||" custom_padding="||40px|||"]<p><span class="review-full-text hide-focus-ring" tabindex="-1">In 2019 I fell extremely ill and lost over 9kgs in 2 days. I was admitted to hospital and remained there for 14days. After many tests nothing was diagnosed. A couple of months later I decided to move to Sydney where I had some more tests. Immediately they found trace of a parasite.</span></p>
<p>My health had deteriorated rapidly, I had no energy, moody,tired,headaches,poor circulation the list was endless. I found it very hard to deal with because before that I was training six days a week and running 10k and 21k races etc.</p>
<p>Matt @ Digestive Wellness came on recommendation to me. After my consultation we introduced a plan of supplements and dietary to work with over the coming months.</p>
<p>Just 2 weeks in I noticed a big change in how I was starting to feel for the better. My energy levels have started to lift again almost immediately, so I was absolutely stoked with that and that gave me the will to push harder towards our final goal of getting me back to where I was before I fell ill. So a little over a year later I have never felt better, sleeping, eating, training again and just feeling so good in myself.</p>
<p>I would highly recommend Matt to anyone! I felt from my consultation the weight of the past number of months had just been lifted because Matt was so knowledgeable about his findings and the plan that was immediately implemented. A massive thank you Matt I cannot thank you enough.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h1><span style="color: #008080;"><strong>Kenn (Qld, Australia)</strong></span></h1>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3>Â </h3>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong><span class="review-full-text hide-focus-ring" tabindex="-1">'So a little over a year later I have never felt better, sleeping, eating, training again and just feeling so good in myself.'</span></strong></h3>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Kenn</strong></h3>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" _builder_version="4.0.6" custom_margin="-107px|||||"][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.0.6" custom_padding="25px|||||"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="4.0.6"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.7.7"]<p><span class="review-full-text hide-focus-ring" tabindex="-1">After getting sick on a trip to India over 5 years ago, and more recently taking a course of Roaccutane Iâ€™ve struggled with severe upper abdominal bloating and cramping almost immediately after eating. It got to the point where I was avoiding eating at restaurants and even wearing jeans. I was left feeling lost and after multiple unsuccessful courses of antibiotics and an IBS diagnosis, </span></p>
<p><span class="review-full-text hide-focus-ring" tabindex="-1">I thought that things wouldnâ€™t change for me. It is hard to put into words how happy I am with the improvements I've seen thanks to Matt. I genuinely feel like I have my life back. I feel so much more confident and have since been able to reintroduce foods I haven't been able to eat for years. Matt is extremely empathetic, knowledgeable and from our first interaction was able to clearly articulate the areas of focus for treatment and the multiple options available to me. </span></p>
<p><span class="review-full-text hide-focus-ring" tabindex="-1">Matt has a wealth of knowledge about gastrointestinal issues and is able to communicate it in an easy to understand way. Throughout my treatment, Matt has been my biggest advocate and has kept me on track and my results are a testament to his commitment and guidance. Thank you Matt!</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h1><span style="color: #008080;"><strong>Rachel (NSW, Australia)</strong></span></h1>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong><span class="review-full-text hide-focus-ring" tabindex="-1">'I genuinely feel like I have my life back. I feel so much more confident and have since been able to reintroduce foods I haven't been able to eat for years.'</span></strong></h3>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Rachel</strong></h3>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" _builder_version="4.0.6" min_height="701px" custom_padding="31px|||||"][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.0.6"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="4.0.6"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.7.7"]<p><span class="review-full-text hide-focus-ring" tabindex="-1">Matt has been a godsend for me and I am constantly recommending him to others with digestive health problems. I had struggled with IBS-D symptoms for so long that I canâ€™t even remember when it started. Iâ€™d seen many different doctors and had been on a low FODMAP diet for over 5 years, which had helped to ease the symptoms, but over time these had continued to worsen and other problems had emerged.</span></p>
<p>In desperation, I found Matt and via phone consultations between my home in Queensland and his office in Sydney he turned it all around. Having far more knowledge than anyone else I had seen, he was able to quickly identify I had SIBO (confirmed by a test). His approach was evidence-based, the treatment was specific to the problems I was experiencing, and his support materials were excellent.</p>
<p><span class="review-full-text hide-focus-ring" tabindex="-1"> I can now eat normally without being constantly bloated, having abdominal pain, or needing to run to the bathroom! Also, as an added bonus, the treatment fixed menstrual problems I had always experienced (e.g. painful &amp; irregular periods, menstrual migraines). Mattâ€™s advice has made such a difference and Iâ€™m so incredibly grateful for his help.</span></p>
